get.description:
This endpoint returns all maps in the account. You can expand the results to include layer details with `expand["layer"]`. Results paginated.

Example request:
```
curl --location --request GET 'https://api.mapulus.com/api/v1/maps' \
--header 'Content-Type: application/json' \
--header 'Authorization: Bearer <your-token>' \
--data '{
          "expand": ["layer"]
        }'
}'

This endpoint returns a single locations on a map when provided a valid map id. You can expand the results to include layer details with `expand["layer"]`.

Example request:
```
curl --location --request GET 'https://api.mapulus.com/api/v1/maps/<map-id>' \
--header 'Content-Type: application/json' \
--header 'Authorization: Bearer <your-token>' \
--data '{
          "expand": ["layer"]
        }'
}'
